Well, I worked for another one of the gigs that I had. I worked for iHeartRadio

wanted a 22 minute long video to be on YouTube. You know, the algorithm has changed and now that's
in style. Interesting. Look at this. Well, let get the blue moonlight and then you get,

about all we paid. I think I bought some pizzas one night. That was it. I bought a box fan from
Walmart to have my friend Todd get chewed up in. I think so. Yeah, the budget was probably like 50
bucks. Rocky, this was fun, man. I've got to take my kids to a trash panda's game, but thanks for

those types of areas, but it's interesting to know that that exists. And a lot of times things are
different than what people think they are. Very, very true. Yeah, this was fun. I appreciate you guys
giving me a call. Yeah. And I particularly am taking away from this conversation and
appreciation that a lot of the things that might make people feel like they don't measure up,
that might make people feel like they should be self conscious and they're not cool enough or
attractive enough are absolutely fake. Hey, you're probably cooler than you think. Absolutely. Cool.
Thanks, man. Thanks guys.
